description: Good for a quick breaky or lunch or dinner.
name: Long Bread Pizza Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 onion, mushroom, ham or bacon, or filling of your choice
1 pkt Woolworths crusty jumbo long bread rolls
1 tsp bbq smoky herb and spices, cayenne pepper

recipeInstructions.text: Put in the oven for 58 min. or until it is cooked thru but not burn the bread. Cool a couple mins before indulging so as not to burn your mouth and tongue. Enjoy!
